Bt m 5 Tips bo qun nn thm ng cch
Cch bo qun nn thm nghe c v n gin, nhung khng phi ai cng bit.
Hu ht nhiu bn hay c thi quen i mi hng cho nn mi ngy, sau khng
y np v mt gc th nn thng s b gim tui th s dng:
S c mt s mo nh khc c th tng tui th ca nn chnh l hc cch bo
qun nn. gi cho nn ca bn bn lu, Mc xin a ra mt s mo nh v cch
bo qun nn thm ng cch khi khng s dng nh.
1. Cch bo qun nn c bn
1.1. Tm quan trng ca an ton chy n
Lu quan trng nht khi s dng nn thm chnh l s dng v bo qun nn sao
cho an ton. Bi v nn thm n cha nguy c ha hon tim n, nn chng phi
c ct gi trnh xa tr em v vt nui, ngay c khi khng s dng. V c nhiu tr
em t m t t nn thm ngay khi bn khng c nh.
Thm vo , bn nn ct nn thm y np trong hp ng, y kn. V lun
nh rng, khng bao gi ngn nn ang chy m khng kim sot.
1.2. Bo qun nn nhit phng
Khi khng s dng nn cn trnh bo qun chng ni c nhit cao, m p,
thch hp nht l nn nhit phng. Nu khng bo qun iu kin thch
hp, nn c th tr nn mm, un cong (cc loi nn tr) v thm ch l tan chy.
Nhng cc bn cng phi ch , khng bo qun nn nhit qu thp, c bit
c nhiu bn khng bit cn nn thm vo trong t lnh. Lm nh vy th nn thm
c th b h khi hp th qu nhiu m hoc b ng bng.
Mt s ni cn trnh bo qun nn nh: gn bp nu, trong t lnh, cnh bn
cc cy nn ang chy khc
Cc loi nn ng trong cc s d bo qun hn so vi nn cy hay nn to hnh v
chng c lp ly cch nhit v d b chy mt cht th chng cng khng b bin i
hnh dng.
1.3. Trnh xa nh sng mt tri
D rng vic cc nn ra nng s lm cy nn ca bn lung linh hn v gip bn
c c nhng tm nh p th Heny vn khuyn bn nn cn nhc. V nhit t nh
sng mt tri c th lm tan chy sp, phai mu nn v mt mi tinh du.
Do , Mc khuyn khch nn ct nn ca bn trong k ng hoc t sch, trnh
xa tia UV ca mt tri. V c bn, khng gian cng ti th ngn nn ca bn cng gi
c lu.
1.4. Trnh cc khu vc m t
Mo cui cng, hy bo qun nn nhng ni kh ro bn nh. C rt nhiu bn s
dng nn khi tm v bo qun nn trong phng tm, kiu nh t nn thm trong nh
tm v qun trong lun.
Mc d iu ny tin li cho mi ln s dng trong nhng ngy t chm sc bn thn,
ni bn th gin bng cch ngm mnh trong bn su, nhng hy trnh ct chng
gn bn ra tay, ni c th xy ra r r hoc b nc bn vo nn thm.
Bn cng nn trnh nhng tng hm m thp.
1.5. Hy bo m t nn thm trong khong thi gian t 20
pht n 4 gi.
Khi bn ln u tin s dng nn, hy m bo t lin tc trong t nht 1 ting
nn chy u tng cnh. Vic ny gip trnh tnh trng bc nn b tht vo v d dng
thp nn ln sau. i vi thi gian ti u tn hng hng thm ca nn, nn gi
thi gian t nn trong khong t 20 pht n 4 gi.
t nn qu t c th lm cho lng h sp tan chy khng u v gy kh khn khi
thp nn ln sau. Ngc li, t nn qu lu c th lm cho sp nn ng li v lm
bt tc bc, cng nh to ra kh carbon khng tt cho sc khe. V vy, hy m bo
bn tun th thi gian t nn c gi c tri nghim tt nht.
